<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Bratislava</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen der zu Bratislava hinterlassenen Habe des verstorbenen Burkhard Sebach mit, dessen Schwester zu Nürnberg benachrichtigt zu haben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_147" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_147_r1l15">Dem <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd dem Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l16">der Stat ʒu Preſſburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_147_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des verpotts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ auf <expan>Burk<ex>art</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l18">ſebachs <expan>ſelıg<ex>en</ex></expan> hab mıt recht bey eẅch 
<del rend="strikethrough">kome </del> ʒu Preſſburg <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l20">darnach <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> rechten <expan>erfunde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> ſey / das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_147_r1l19">Jr das </ab></add> ın <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rate ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l21">
<add>ſüllet</add> tun etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l22"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır erfarn <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>burk<ex>art</ex></expan> ſebach ſelıg ein <expan>ſweſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l23">bey vns hat / der <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch wır eẅr <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> alſo ʒu <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l25">getan vnd erfürn 
<add><ab facs="#facs_147_r1l24">wır </ab></add> ıcht mer <expan>erbe<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe er bey vns hett den <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l26">wır das auch ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> tun / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_147_r1l27"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> margarete </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_147" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> und dem rate der stat zu Pressburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des verpotts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz auf
                            <expan>Burk<ex>art</ex></expan> Sebachs <expan>selig<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        hab mit recht bey ewch zu Pressburg <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        darnach <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> rechten <expan>erfunde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> sey, das <add>ir das</add> in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> rate zu
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>süllet</add> tun etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir erfarn
                        <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>Burk<ex>art</ex></expan> Sebach selig ein
                            <expan>swest<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns hat, der
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch wir ewr
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> also zu
                                <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan> getan und erfürn <add>wir</add> icht
                        mer <expan>erbe<ex>n</ex></expan>, die er bey uns hett, den
                                <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir das auch zu
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> tun. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Margarete.</ab>
</div>
